\s Vika Mwokozi Taji
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Vika Mwokozi \bd*\bd Taji\bd*\bd , \bd*\bd Kondoo \bd*\bd na Mufalme, Majeshi yote ya\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni wanasifu sana\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Ee nafsi yangu, sifu aliyekukufia, Mufalme wako, Bwana kwa milele na milele.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Vika Mwokozi taji, ni Bwana wa mapendo, Vidonda vyake utazame kwa mikono yake. Ni \bd*\bd Neema\bd*\bd  kubwa sana kwa watu wa makosa, Ee tunashangilia sana, tunamutukuza.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Vika Mwokozi taji, ni Bwana wa uzima, Aliyetoka kaburini, aliyefufuka. Tunamwimbia sifa kwake aliyekufa Kutuletea ukombozi, yuko hai milele.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Vika Mwokozi taji, ni Bwana wa\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni, Aliyetuma Roho kwetu toka Baba \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd . Tutoe sifa kwako uliyetukufia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Ee Bwana wetu, utukuzwe sasa na milele.\bd*
